    "body": "One cannot submit a normal zksync transaction without changing the active network in Metamask. However, you can submit so-called \"priority\" operation this way: it will be stored in zksync L1 contract, our server will pick it up from there and execute. However, this is much more expensive, as you need to pay for L1 gas.",
